Direct result: `cognitive-kernels` is a Node.js (ESM) + TypeScript monorepo that integrates LLM providers (Claude + OpenAI/Codex), an MCP control-plane server, a runs API server (Hono), and an optional Neon Postgres backend (Drizzle ORM + neon-http), plus a WebSocket “Lens” observability server.

